        <p>The Services provided by the Foundation are intended for informational and educational purposes only. The content, which includes but is not limited to articles, videos, course materials, presentations, text, graphics, logos, and software ("Content"), is designed to advance professional and public understanding of restorative reproductive medicine.</p>

